{
  "texts": [
    "This description of the filtering process facilitates the credibility of the work.",
    "Also, new researchers can follow or tune the query to review more updated papers for an extended period.",
    "• We classify the fairness issues first and then further classify the fairness-ensuring methodologies adopted to solve each type of fairness issue.",
    "We also represent the graphical taxonomy of fairness issues in Fig. 6, the taxonomy of methodologies in Fig.",
    "7, and a taxonomy representing specific methodologies targeted to solve specific issues and their limitations in Fig. 10 for researchers to understand this area's current trends easily."
  ]
}